+| Maximum vertical speed | `1.0 m/s` commanded slew | Rate-limit changes in NED `z`. |
+| Target jump limit | `1.5 m` per received command | Split larger jumps into intermediate setpoints or reject them. |
+| Target timeout | `1.0 s` for streaming clients | Hold last safe target when command input expires. |
