+
+### `/uav/target_position`
+
+Type: `geometry_msgs/msg/Point`
+
+Fields:
+
+| Field | Meaning |
+| --- | --- |
+| `x` | Target north position in local NED, meters. |
+| `y` | Target east position in local NED, meters. |
+| `z` | Target down position in local NED, meters. Use `z=-altitude` for positive height commands. |
